To install daycabs, install cab to frame mounting bolts and nuts at front and rear mounting locations. Refer to (Figure 97)
for Install Daycab Front Cab Mounting. Refer to (Figure 97)
for Install Daycab Rear Cab Air Suspension Mounting.

To Install short sleeper cabs, install cab to frame mounting bolts and nuts at front and rear mounting locations. Refer to (Figure 98)
for Install Short Sleeper Cab Front Cab Mounting. Refer to (Figure 98)
for Install Short Sleeper Cab Rear Cab Air Suspension Mounting.

To Install long sleeper cabs, install cab to frame mounting bolts and nuts at front and rear mounting locations. Refer to (Figure 99)
for Install Long Sleeper Cab Front Cab Mounting. Refer to (Figure 99)
for Install Long Sleeper Cab Rear Cab Air Suspension Mounting.
